<section class="opa-section opa-dark opa-faq" id="faq">
  <div class="opa-container">
    <p class="opa-eyebrow opa-reveal">Questions</p>
    <h2 class="opa-h1 opa-reveal">Every objection,<br><span class="opa-italic">answered straight</span>.</h2>

    <div class="opa-faq__layout">
      <nav class="opa-faq__nav opa-reveal" aria-label="FAQ categories">
        <a href="#faq-c1" class="is-active">Is it for me</a>
        <a href="#faq-c2">How the Coach works</a>
        <a href="#faq-c3">Time &amp; effort</a>
        <a href="#faq-c4">Money</a>
        <a href="#faq-c5">What you get</a>
        <a href="#faq-c6">After you buy</a>
      </nav>

      <div class="opa-faq__col">

        <div class="opa-faq__group" id="faq-c1">
          <h3 class="opa-faq__h opa-reveal">Is it for me</h3>
          <details class="opa-faq__item opa-reveal">
            <summary class="opa-faq__q"><span>Is this for me?</span><span class="opa-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="opa-faq__a">If you have ideas you don&rsquo;t ship, yes. The protocol is built for people who get stuck in the loop. It removes the decisions that paralyze you and leaves only execution. You don&rsquo;t need experience. You need 14 nights.</div>
          </details>
          <details class="opa-faq__item opa-reveal">
            <summary class="opa-faq__q"><span>I&rsquo;ve never sold anything online.</span><span class="opa-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="opa-faq__a">Perfect &mdash; that&rsquo;s exactly who this is for. You&rsquo;re not starting with a product, you&rsquo;re starting with a person and a problem. The protocol walks you through every step, and the Coach catches you when you wobble. First-timers finish this all the time.</div>
          </details>
          <details class="opa-faq__item opa-reveal">
            <summary class="opa-faq__q"><span>What if I don&rsquo;t have an idea yet?</span><span class="opa-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="opa-faq__a">Phase 1 handles that. You start with a person, not an idea. You define who you want to serve, then find what they actually struggle with. The idea emerges from real conversations in Phase 2 &mdash; not from your head.</div>
          </details>
        </div>

        <div class="opa-faq__group" id="faq-c2">
          <h3 class="opa-faq__h opa-reveal">How the Coach works</h3>
          <details class="opa-faq__item opa-reveal">
            <summary class="opa-faq__q"><span>What exactly is the Coach?</span><span class="opa-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="opa-faq__a">A Master Prompt you load into free Claude or ChatGPT. Once loaded, the chat knows the full 14-night protocol &mdash; every phase, every night, every template. You use it like a senior operator who already shipped and remembers every step.</div>
          </details>
          <details class="opa-faq__item opa-reveal">
            <summary class="opa-faq__q"><span>How do I use it day to day?</span><span class="opa-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="opa-faq__a">Three steps. Open the night in your Notion portal &mdash; it tells you the objective and the done-check. Paste the Master Prompt into Claude or ChatGPT. Tell the Coach what night you&rsquo;re on and where you&rsquo;re stuck. It gives you the next move, not a lecture.</div>
          </details>
          <details class="opa-faq__item opa-reveal">
            <summary class="opa-faq__q"><span>What does the Coach do when I&rsquo;m stuck?</span><span class="opa-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="opa-faq__a">It diagnoses, then prescribes. No motivational speech. It opens the right template, narrows the next step to something doable in under an hour, and asks you to report back when it&rsquo;s done.</div>
          </details>
        </div>

        <div class="opa-faq__group" id="faq-c3">
          <h3 class="opa-faq__h opa-reveal">Time &amp; effort</h3>
          <details class="opa-faq__item opa-reveal">
            <summary class="opa-faq__q"><span>How much time per night?</span><span class="opa-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="opa-faq__a">1 to 2 hours. Some nights are intense (validation calls), some are short (decision nights). Total over 14 nights is roughly 20 hours. One focused evening at a time.</div>
          </details>
          <details class="opa-faq__item opa-reveal">
            <summary class="opa-faq__q"><span>I have a full-time job &mdash; can I still do it?</span><span class="opa-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="opa-faq__a">Yes. The protocol is built around 1&ndash;2 hour blocks, so it fits an evening or an early morning. You can also stretch the 14 nights into a 21-night calendar. What matters is the sequence, not the speed.</div>
          </details>
          <details class="opa-faq__item opa-reveal">
            <summary class="opa-faq__q"><span>What if I miss a night?</span><span class="opa-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="opa-faq__a">Nothing breaks. The protocol is a sequence, not a schedule. Pick up where you left off. The only rule is you don&rsquo;t skip steps &mdash; each one feeds the next.</div>
          </details>
        </div>

        <div class="opa-faq__group" id="faq-c4">
          <h3 class="opa-faq__h opa-reveal">Money</h3>
          <details class="opa-faq__item opa-reveal">
            <summary class="opa-faq__q"><span>Why is it only $49?</span><span class="opa-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="opa-faq__a">Because it&rsquo;s a system, not a 40-hour course you&rsquo;ll never finish. We&rsquo;d rather it be an easy yes and have you actually ship. One-time payment, lifetime access, no upsells.</div>
          </details>
          <details class="opa-faq__item opa-reveal">
            <summary class="opa-faq__q"><span>Do I need to pay for Claude or ChatGPT?</span><span class="opa-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="opa-faq__a">No. The Coach runs on the free tiers of Claude or ChatGPT. You load one Master Prompt and you&rsquo;re set. No subscription required to complete the 14 nights.</div>
          </details>
          <details class="opa-faq__item opa-reveal">
            <summary class="opa-faq__q"><span>What if it doesn&rsquo;t work &mdash; refund?</span><span class="opa-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="opa-faq__a">Yes. 14-night money-back. If you follow the protocol and don&rsquo;t have a product live by Night 14, email within 30 days. The $49 is returned. No forms, no interrogation.</div>
          </details>
        </div>

        <div class="opa-faq__group" id="faq-c5">
          <h3 class="opa-faq__h opa-reveal">What you get</h3>
          <details class="opa-faq__item opa-reveal">
            <summary class="opa-faq__q"><span>What&rsquo;s included?</span><span class="opa-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="opa-faq__a">Four modules: the complete 17-page protocol, the AI Coach Master Prompt, templates for every phase (audience profile, validation scripts, launch outreach), and binary done/not-done criteria for each night. Delivered as a Notion portal.</div>
          </details>
          <details class="opa-faq__item opa-reveal">
            <summary class="opa-faq__q"><span>How is this different from a course?</span><span class="opa-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="opa-faq__a">Courses teach. This executes. You won&rsquo;t watch hours of video. You&rsquo;ll do one task per night, check a completion box, and move forward. By Night 14 you have a product live. Most courses leave you with notes.</div>
          </details>
          <details class="opa-faq__item opa-reveal">
            <summary class="opa-faq__q"><span>What kind of product will I launch?</span><span class="opa-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="opa-faq__a">One of three formats: a PDF guide, a template pack, or a prompt pack. Phase 1 helps you pick the right format for your audience &mdash; buildable in days, not months.</div>
          </details>
        </div>

        <div class="opa-faq__group" id="faq-c6">
          <h3 class="opa-faq__h opa-reveal">After you buy</h3>
          <details class="opa-faq__item opa-reveal">
            <summary class="opa-faq__q"><span>How do I get access?</span><span class="opa-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="opa-faq__a">Immediately. After payment you get an email with access to the Notion portal. You&rsquo;re inside within 60 seconds and can start Night 1 right away.</div>
          </details>
          <details class="opa-faq__item opa-reveal">
            <summary class="opa-faq__q"><span>Is there support or community?</span><span class="opa-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="opa-faq__a">The AI Coach is your primary guide &mdash; available 24/7 inside Claude or ChatGPT. For account-related matters, email hello@oneproductai.com.</div>
          </details>
          <details class="opa-faq__item opa-reveal">
            <summary class="opa-faq__q"><span>Will this work outside the US?</span><span class="opa-faq__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
            <div class="opa-faq__a">Yes. The protocol works anywhere. Examples use US audiences for market size, but the structure applies to any English-speaking market and uses tools available worldwide.</div>
          </details>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

